contents:
[package]
name = "glyphon"
description = "Fast, simple 2D text rendering for wgpu"
version = "0.3.0"
edition = "2021"
homepage = "https://github.com/grovesNL/glyphon.git"
repository = "https://github.com/grovesNL/glyphon"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0 OR Zlib"

[dependencies]
wgpu = "0.18"
etagere = "0.2.8"
cosmic-text = "0.10"
lru = "0.11"

[dev-dependencies]
winit = "0.28.7"
pollster = "0.3.0"

[package]
name = "iced_core"
description = "The essential ideas of iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
log = "0.4"
thiserror = "1.0"
num-traits = "0.2"
palette = "0.7"

[dev-dependencies]
approx = "0.5"

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.instant]
workspace = true

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.raw-window-handle]
workspace = true

[package]
name = "iced_futures"
description = "Commands, subscriptions, and future executors for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
thread-pool = [ "futures/thread-pool",]

[dependencies]
futures = "0.3"
log = "0.4"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.async-std]
workspace = true
optional = true
features = [ "unstable",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.smol]
workspace = true
optional = true

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio]
workspace = true
optional = true
features = [ "rt", "rt-multi-thread", "time",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.wasm-bindgen-futures]
workspace = true

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.wasm-timer]
workspace = true

[package]
name = "iced_graphics"
description = "A bunch of backend-agnostic types that can be leveraged to build a renderer for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
geometry = [ "lyon_path",]
image = [ "dep:image", "kamadak-exif",]
web-colors = []

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
cosmic-text = "0.10"
glam = "0.24"
half = "2.2"
log = "0.4"
once_cell = "1.0"
raw-window-handle = "0.5"
rustc-hash = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.0"
image = "0.24"
kamadak-exif = "0.5"
lyon_path = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "iced_renderer"
description = "The official renderer for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
wgpu = [ "iced_wgpu",]
image = [ "iced_tiny_skia/image", "iced_wgpu?/image",]
svg = [ "iced_tiny_skia/svg", "iced_wgpu?/svg",]
geometry = [ "iced_graphics/geometry", "iced_tiny_skia/geometry", "iced_wgpu?/geometry",]
tracing = [ "iced_wgpu?/tracing",]
web-colors = [ "iced_wgpu?/web-colors",]
webgl = [ "iced_wgpu?/webgl",]

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
raw-window-handle = "0.5"
thiserror = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.iced_tiny_skia]
version = "0.12"
path = "tiny_skia"

[dependencies.iced_wgpu]
version = "0.12"
path = "wgpu"

[package]
name = "iced_runtime"
description = "A renderer-agnostic runtime for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
debug = []
multi-window = []

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.12"
path = "futures"

[package]
name = "iced_style"
description = "The default set of styles of Iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[dependencies]
palette = "0.7"
once_cell = "1.0"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[package]
name = "iced_tiny_skia"
description = "A software renderer for iced on top of tiny-skia"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
image = [ "iced_graphics/image",]
svg = [ "resvg",]
geometry = [ "iced_graphics/geometry",]

[dependencies]
cosmic-text = "0.10"
kurbo = "0.9"
log = "0.4"
raw-window-handle = "0.5"
rustc-hash = "1.0"
softbuffer = "0.2"
tiny-skia = "0.11"
resvg = "0.36"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.xxhash-rust]
version = "0.8"
features = [ "xxh3",]

[package]
name = "iced_wgpu"
description = "A renderer for iced on top of wgpu"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
geometry = [ "iced_graphics/geometry", "lyon",]
image = [ "iced_graphics/image",]
svg = [ "resvg",]
web-colors = [ "iced_graphics/web-colors",]
webgl = [ "wgpu/webgl",]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
futures = "0.3"
glam = "0.24"
guillotiere = "0.6"
log = "0.4"
once_cell = "1.0"
raw-window-handle = "0.5"
wgpu = "0.18"
lyon = "1.0"
resvg = "0.36"
tracing = "0.1"

[dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[dependencies.bytemuck]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.glyphon]
git = "https://github.com/grovesNL/glyphon.git"
rev = "2caa9fc5e5923c1d827d177c3619cab7e9885b85"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "iced_widget"
description = "The built-in widgets for iced"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
lazy = [ "ouroboros",]
image = [ "iced_renderer/image",]
svg = [ "iced_renderer/svg",]
canvas = [ "iced_renderer/geometry",]
qr_code = [ "canvas", "qrcode",]
wgpu = [ "iced_renderer/wgpu",]

[dependencies]
num-traits = "0.2"
thiserror = "1.0"
unicode-segmentation = "1.0"
ouroboros = "0.17"

[dependencies.iced_renderer]
version = "0.12"
path = "renderer"

[dependencies.iced_runtime]
version = "0.12"
path = "runtime"

[dependencies.iced_style]
version = "0.12"
path = "style"

[dependencies.qrcode]
version = "0.12"
default-features = false

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]
all-features = true

[package]
name = "mpeg_encoder"
version = "0.2.1"
authors = [ "Sébastien Crozet <developer@crozet.re>",]
edition = "2021"
description = "A simple ffmpeg video encoder."
repository = "https://github.com/sebcrozet/mpeg_encoder"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "encoder", "ffmpeg", "mpeg", "video",]
license = "BSD-3-Clause"

[features]
default = []
build = [ "ffmpeg-sys/build",]

[dependencies.ffmpeg-sys]
package = "ffmpeg-sys-next"
version = "6.0.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "avformat", "swscale",]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/grovesnl/glyphon"]
git = "https://github.com/grovesnl/glyphon"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "2caa9fc5e5923c1d827d177c3619cab7e9885b85"

[source."https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"]
git = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "fc285d3e461626408c56bbc1605fcf0c974b2f69"

[source."https://github.com/polymeilex/mpeg_encoder_next"]
git = "https://github.com/polymeilex/mpeg_encoder_next"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
